Updated `website/src/css/custom.css` to stabilize the Transit navbar shell itself.

Header-shell changes:
- `.navbar` now declares `width: 100%`
- `.navbar__surface` now declares `width: 100%`
- `.navbar__inner` now stays `flex-wrap: nowrap`
- nav items and links now use `white-space: nowrap`

These rules prevent the multi-line wrapped header state that caused the page body to overlap the bottom of the navbar.
